Micropolis Corp said it filed with theSecurities and Exchange Commission a registration statementcovering a 75 mln dlr issue of convertible subordinateddebentures due 2012.    Proceeds will be used for general corporate purposes andpossible acquisitions, Micropolis said.    The company named Kidder, Peabody and Co Inc as leadmanager, and Robertson, Colman and Stephens as co-manager ofthe offering. Reuter&#3;